The murder trial of Senzo Meyiwa has been postponed until Monday. State witness Thabo Mosia said he was feeling unwell which forced the postponement. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Things got a bit heated between Judge Tshifhiwa Maumela and Advocate Malesela Teffo at the murder trial of Senzo Meyiwa. Judge Maumela reprimanded Teffo, telling him that he won't dictate how he runs the trial. READ: WATCH | Senzo Meyiwa murder trial postponed to Monday Teffo represents four of the suspects accused of murdering Meyiwa. The trial has been postponed until Monday. State witness Thabo Mosia said he was feeling unwell which forced the postponement.